events.name: Nebraska Cornhuskers at Rutgers Scarlet Knights

headlines.description: — While he may have been the last player to get back on the field after halftime, a banged-up Nebraska quarterback Casey Thompson was center stage in the final 30 minutes.
headlines.shortLinkText: Thompson throws 2 TDs, Nebraska rallies to beat Rutgers

headlines.description: — Clayton Tune threw a pair of touchdown passes inside the final two minutes as Houston scored 26 fourth-quarter points to stun Memphis 33-32 on Friday night.
headlines.shortLinkText: Tune throws 2 TD passes late, Houston stuns Memphis 33-32

events.name: Colorado State Rams at Nevada Wolf Pack

headlines.description: — Michael Boyle kicked a 43-yard field goal on an untimed down at the end of the game to lift Colorado State over Nevada 17-14 on Friday night...
headlines.shortLinkText: Boyle's 2nd-chance FG to end game snaps Rams' 10-game skid

events.name: UNLV Rebels at San José State Spartans

headlines.description: — Chevan Cordeiro accounted for four touchdowns to lead San Jose State to a 40-7 rout of UNLV on Friday night.
headlines.shortLinkText: Cordeiro accounts for 4 TDs, San Jose State routs UNLV 40-7
